Notes

This version has disc face 'BIEM / MCPS' Rights Societies, matrix SID Codes and is pressed by 'Disctronics'. No 'Compact Disc' logo is present. Four other versions exist with the same Cat#: The very first version with no disc face 'Compact Disc' logo or SID Codes and has UK 'PDO' pressing plant matrix info is [url=http://www.discogs.com/Orbital-Orbital/release/1684136]here[/url]. The version with German pressing plant info in the disc matrix area and the Cat# '828 386-2' printed in the fold-out booklet is [url=http://www.discogs.com/Orbital-Orbital-2-Brown-Album/release/1684932]here[/url] The post 1994 version with disc face 'BIEM / MCPS' Rights Societies, no 'Compact Disc' logo, has SID Codes and 'PMDC' pressing plant info is [url=http://www.discogs.com/Orbital-Orbital-2-Brown-Album/release/4527696]here[/url] The post 1994 version with disc face 'BIEM/STEMRA' Rights Societies, SID Codes and UK 'PMDC' pressing plant matrix info is [url=http://www.discogs.com/Orbital-Orbital-2-Brown-Album/release/4468091]here[/url]. The copyright in this sound recording is owned by Internal Records. ℗© 1993 INTERNAL Incidental information: There are minor variations to the durations printed on the insert.
